member.summary:
Create a new RenderSourceView for the given doc.
Note that this should be done with using(var rsv = new RenderSourceView(doc)) {}
If the RenderSettings have the source view set to for instance a SnapShot this construct will ensure that the (active) view is set to the correct snapshot, and reverted back to the original once this instance goes out of scope.

